headline: 3 Reasons to Sell CBRE and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: CBRE trades at $127.50 per share and has moved almost in lockstep with the market over the last six months. The stock has lost 5.9% while the S&P 500 is down 2.1%. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
